room_title: Escape room "The Study" by West Palm Beach Escape Rooms in West Palm Beach
room_address: 209 S. Olive Ave West Palm Beach, FL 33401
room_description: When you arrive at the cabin, you find an abandoned home with unfinished experiments and paperwork leading you to a clock counting down to zero. Can your group of Escape Room Adventurists finding the lost prized painting? One hour is all that separates you from making history or being history!
